    <item>
      <title>随着芯片股上涨，日本股市可能连续第三天上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/japan-s-stocks-may-rise-for-third-day-as-chip-shares-advance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国通胀降温的迹象抑制了人们对美联储下个月降息的猜测，日本股市可能延续上周历史性暴跌后的反弹势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/japan-s-stocks-may-rise-for-third-day-as-chip-shares-advance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:05:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀数据再次温和上涨，巩固美联储降息决心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/us-cpi-data-to-show-another-modest-increase-cementing-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预测人士预计，美国月度消费者价格报告将显示上个月再次出现小幅上涨，这增强了人们对美联储 9 月份降息的普遍预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/us-cpi-data-to-show-another-modest-increase-cementing-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国4800万套未完工房屋或将延长危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/china-has-sold-at-least-48-million-homes-that-aren-t-even-built</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博行业研究报告显示，中国至少有 4800 万套房屋在竣工前被出售，这意味着中国的房地产危机不会很快得到解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/china-has-sold-at-least-48-million-homes-that-aren-t-even-built</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市将在 CPI 倒计时中跟随美国股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新的美国通胀数据强化了人们对美联储将于 9 月份开始实施广泛预期的货币宽松政策的猜测，亚洲股市将跟随华尔街上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 22:30:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
